= TTF_GlyphMetrics =

Get the metrics (dimensions) of a glyph To understand what these metrics mean, here is a useful link: http://freetype.sourceforge.net/freetype2/docs/tutorial/step2.html 

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int TTF_GlyphMetrics(TTF_Font *font, Uint16 ch,
                     int *minx, int *maxx,
                     int *miny, int *maxy, int *advance);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|-
|'''ch'''
|char index, 16bits
|}

